1. inline css
2. internal css
3. external css

Examples:

INLINE:  <p style="color:red;font-size:15px">

INTERNAL:  <head>
              <title> ... </title>
              <style>
                 h1{
                    color:green;
                    background:yellow;
                   }
                 p{
                   color:yellow:
                  }
              </style>
           </head>
           
EXTERNAL:  <head>
              <title> ... </title>
              <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" type="text/css"/>
           </head>
           
           
           style.css file:
                h1{
                    color:green;
                    background:yellow;
                   }
                 p{
                   color:yellow:
                  }
           
